dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Laguna Seca Ranch and Hammonds Ranch quadrangles, Fresno and Merced counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: Laguna Seca Ranch and Hammonds Ranch map
Geology Laguna Seca Ranch and Hammonds Ranch quadrangle
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Laguna Seca Ranch, CA 1956, photorevised 1971, DMA 1857 IV SE -- series V895; Hammonds Ranch, CA 1956, photorevised 1984, DMA 1857 I SW -- series V895."
Includes location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1974.
